      <title>“不安分”的斯塔默称新政府必须推动变革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/-restless-starmer-says-new-government-must-get-on-with-change</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默表示，周四英国大选选民赋予政府“变革授权”，新内阁必须“立即行动起来”，注重兑现承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/-restless-starmer-says-new-government-must-get-on-with-change</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 13:47:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管辩论失利，拜登在摇摆州缩小与特朗普的差距</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-07-06/biden-narrows-trump-s-election-lead-in-key-states-after-debate-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻社/晨间咨询公司显示，尽管有十分之三的民主党人表示他应该退出竞选，但这位现任总统在关键州的支持率仅落后于他的共和党对手 2 个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-07-06/biden-narrows-trump-s-election-lead-in-key-states-after-debate-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 13:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默确认英国将终止苏纳克的卢旺达驱逐政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/starmer-confirms-uk-to-end-sunak-s-rwanda-deportation-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默表示，新工党政府将废除前任里希·苏纳克将寻求庇护者驱逐至卢旺达的计划，这表明他打算采取新的移民政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/starmer-confirms-uk-to-end-sunak-s-rwanda-deportation-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 12:44:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前谢里夫盟友组建新政党以改变巴基斯坦政局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/former-sharif-ally-forms-new-party-to-change-pakistan-s-politics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在民众对政府紧缩措施日益不满的背景下，巴基斯坦前总理沙希德·哈坎·阿巴斯于周六成立了一个新政党，这是他与该国强大的谢里夫家族闹翻的结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/former-sharif-ally-forms-new-party-to-change-pakistan-s-politics</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 11:33:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登坚持竞选，但党内质疑声依然存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/biden-clings-to-campaign-but-skepticism-among-allies-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登度过了竞选重置中最关键的一天，避免了在关键的黄金时段采访中出现重大失误，并在威斯康星州喧闹的集会上赢得了热烈欢迎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/biden-clings-to-campaign-but-skepticism-among-allies-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党的 100 亿英镑危机法案只是第一个财政挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/labour-s-10-billion-crisis-bill-just-the-first-fiscal-challenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工党自 2010 年以来首次重返政府，并承诺将立即实施修复经济的计划。首先它需要找到资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/labour-s-10-billion-crisis-bill-just-the-first-fiscal-challenge</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>执政党称台湾前副总理正在接受调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/former-taiwanese-vice-premier-under-probe-ruling-party-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾执政党表示，前副总理郑文灿正在接受检察机关调查，当地媒体报道称，这位资深政治人物因涉嫌腐败而接受调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/former-taiwanese-vice-premier-under-probe-ruling-party-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 03:56:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗选出希望与西方重启核谈判的总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/reformist-pezeshkian-elected-president-of-iran-state-tv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[69 岁的心脏外科医生马苏德·佩泽什基安 (Masoud Pezeshkian) 希望与美国重启具有里程碑意义的核协议谈判，他在这场突显伊朗国内外面临的重大挑战的选举中当选为伊朗总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/reformist-pezeshkian-elected-president-of-iran-state-tv</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 03:18:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院民主党领袖将于周末举行会议，因焦虑情绪加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/top-house-democrat-to-hold-weekend-meeting-amid-biden-anxieties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于民主党对乔·拜登是否应该继续参加总统竞选的忧虑日益加剧，众议院少数党领袖哈基姆·杰弗里斯周五晚突然安排了一次不寻常的周末会议，与民主党高层同僚会面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/top-house-democrat-to-hold-weekend-meeting-amid-biden-anxieties</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 00:30:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
